      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with no swirls, chips, or imperfections, and the interior is pristine, showing zero signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, and the car has been maintained with the utmost care. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom-quality condition.",
